Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.54,0:03:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司 快起來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.96,0:03:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早安 天亮了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.71,0:03:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.80,0:03:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我…我因為要去洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.87,0:03:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.55,0:03:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.23,0:03:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.74,0:03:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}話說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.01,0:03:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.06,0:04:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉你會不會有時候 希望我們一起出去吃個飯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.97,0:04:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}之類的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.95,0:04:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.35,0:04:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司會開心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.29,0:04:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 會的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.18,0:04:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那麼就去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.95,0:04:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.94,0:04:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.08,0:04:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不用謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.15,0:04:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我幫你再添一點喝的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.41,0:04:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.39,0:04:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對對對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.22,0:04:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抹布 抹布
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.98,0:04:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這樣啊 藥草都用完了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.50,0:04:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 司喜歡的那個墨角蘭茶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.41,0:04:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要再去買了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.27,0:05:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.05,0:05:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那麼工作結束後去買吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.02,0:05:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個…我們一起
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.01,0:05:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.57,0:05:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早安唷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.82,0:05:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看到沒看到沒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.92,0:05:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不覺得剛剛這兩個人好像正要牽手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.39,0:05:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}別那麼招搖好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.96,0:05:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你好像在生氣呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.05,0:05:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒有的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.78,0:05:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不過話說回來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.67,0:05:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我覺得自己實在太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.06,0:05:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我居然沒能聽到艾拉拉驚人的告白台詞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.05,0:05:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉拉能不能在我面前再向司司告白一次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.94,0:05:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這輩子唯一的請求了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.95,0:05:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好嘛 好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.97,0:05:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.99,0:05:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒看到艾拉很困擾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.47,0:05:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.22,0:05:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}老實說艾拉的做法並不是什麼值得讚揚的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.15,0:06:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明明是工作時間居然去告白什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.49,0:06:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}滿嘴上雖然這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.60,0:06:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是昨晚一個人神魂顛倒的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.74,0:06:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}「我也好想那樣浪漫的告白」什麼什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.58,0:06:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 不對不是想告白而是想被告白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.36,0:06:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂 別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.59,0:06:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}滿滿早晚也會遇到你的白馬王子的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.70,0:06:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你一定是在嘲笑我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.90,0:06:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早啊 兩位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.00,0:06:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}昨晚睡得好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.18,0:06:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還是根本沒怎麼睡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.50,0:06:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你在說…說…說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.02,0:06:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我們連K…K…KISS都還沒有過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.89,0:06:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那一定是度過了一個苦悶的夜晚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.45,0:06:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂 你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.57,0:06:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}康孝 這種玩笑太惡劣了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.19,0:06:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他們倆已經是公司內部公認的一對了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.71,0:06:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以才要捉弄一下才好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.34,0:07:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼歪理
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.00,0:07:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司和艾拉都不要理他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.17,0:07:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是正經啊 不愧是我親愛的搭檔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.92,0:07:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}話說司 有件重要的事要告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.40,0:07:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.01,0:07:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和戀人順利發展的秘訣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.24,0:07:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是要不時的用心製造驚喜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.26,0:07:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}驚喜…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.58,0:07:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒錯 無論何時
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.06,0:07:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}女生都會期盼著浪漫的驚喜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.51,0:07:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想體驗當公主的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.10,0:07:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.10,0:07:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司 可別太當真
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.79,0:07:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然你這麼說 其實雪莉你也在期待著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.61,0:07:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這種驚喜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.19,0:07:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉 我能問個問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.40,0:07:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.52,0:07:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要怎樣才能喜歡上自己的搭檔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.17,0:07:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喜歡什麼的…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.49,0:08:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}矮油 聽上去好像雪莉不喜歡我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.06,0:08:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}連上班都遲到的搭檔怎麼喜歡的起來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.56,0:08:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 和營業部翔子醬約會的時間到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.13,0:08:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這種時候倒是很守時啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.36,0:08:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.29,0:08:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我們稍微談談吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.38,0:08:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你們倆要好好的發展喲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.70,0:08:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}驚喜 驚喜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.18,0:08:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}驚喜…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.59,0:08:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘀咕什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.11,0:08:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.30,0:08:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早！安！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.64,0:08:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}香月只是在吃醋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.68,0:08:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}原諒她吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.89,0:08:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小艾拉 麻煩泡杯茶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.46,0:08:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天也是夫人親手做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.85,0:08:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.89,0:08:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}她幫你做便當 你開心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.33,0:08:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那當然
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.82,0:09:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}內人還會考慮營養平衡的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.76,0:09:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.17,0:09:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}已經十幾年沒人幫我做便當了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.06,0:09:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哦呀？哦呀哦呀哦呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.19,0:09:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}難道小艾拉想幫司做便當？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.63,0:09:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這這這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.51,0:09:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且我一次都沒做過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.87,0:09:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}讓滿教你如何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.81,0:09:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那傢伙很會做飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.36,0:09:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}驚喜！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.79,0:09:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}能讓女生高興的驚喜到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.81,0:09:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然還是花束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.02,0:09:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可是之前不是失敗過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.63,0:09:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}從背後頂膝蓋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.59,0:09:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那哪是驚喜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.61,0:09:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是捉弄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.84,0:09:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}帶她去吃豪華晚餐怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.08,0:09:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}她好像對吃的沒什麼興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.61,0:09:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}做鬼臉怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.61,0:09:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉很擅長做這些
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.72,0:09:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是說了是讓女生高興的事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.13,0:10:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}話說…咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.43,0:10:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉很擅長做鬼臉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.59,0:10:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}很噁心的那種
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.50,0:10:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}噁心啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.54,0:10:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是什麼樣的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.39,0:10:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這樣 還是這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.32,0:10:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}或者……
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.61,0:10:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}現在的司也很噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.36,0:10:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看起來很幸福就夠了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.89,0:10:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}找我秘密商量？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.05,0:10:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}難道和司有關嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.96,0:10:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.53,0:10:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好吧 正好我也有事要問你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.21,0:10:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}實際上和戀人一起生活是什麼感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.08,0:10:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼什麼感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.62,0:10:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}成為戀…戀…戀人前後 有什麼不一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.64,0:10:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 難道昨天已經K…K…KISS了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.80,0:10:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊不不不不 這太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.55,0:10:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不過等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.71,0:10:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你們一直都住在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.80,0:11:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和普通情侶比起來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.22,0:11:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}進展快速也沒什麼奇怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.05,0:11:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再說晚上也睡在同一個房間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.78,0:11:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}難道不只親親 還有更進一步的！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.42,0:11:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不知為什麼 成為戀人後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.35,0:11:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不能像以前那樣順暢的交流了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.67,0:11:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.02,0:11:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.61,0:11:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看你的樣子 大概也能想像
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.97,0:11:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以想請你教我做飯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.65,0:11:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}原來如此 是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.58,0:11:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想做給那傢伙吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.59,0:11:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想讓他高興嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.57,0:11:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}然後想著就能像以前那樣愉快的交談了對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.05,0:11:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是精神可嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.82,0:12:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好吧 我來教你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.57,0:12:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那你想做什麼樣的料理呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.11,0:12:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.84,0:12:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你想啊 你要根據司的喜好來決定做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.07,0:12:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哦… 司喜歡吃什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.57,0:12:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你問我 我也不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.91,0:12:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}竟然連這種事情都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.37,0:12:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我真是不配做他的女朋友
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.10,0:12:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真慢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.42,0:12:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}午休不是早就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.99,0:12:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.21,0:12:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉說有事情要問你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.69,0:12:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.33,0:12:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.03,0:12:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}錯誤 沒有聽清楚  請再說一…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.05,0:12:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都到現在了你還害羞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.71,0:12:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.35,0:12:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個…到底發生什麼事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.22,0:12:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉說要為你做飯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.96,0:12:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以你想吃什麼就說出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.56,0:12:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什…！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.24,0:13:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要維持好戀人關係的秘訣就是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.94,0:13:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}時刻要準備著驚喜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.26,0:13:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這難道是 艾拉給我準備的驚喜！？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.65,0:13:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}被搶先了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.04,0:13:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂 你在聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.17,0:13:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.74,0:13:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉的心意我非常高興
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.79,0:13:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是如果只是單方面的被給予
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.77,0:13:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我會很不好意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.74,0:13:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今早說的那個事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.04,0:13:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也只是想和艾拉吃個飯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.57,0:13:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那如果兩個人一起做飯就好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.02,0:13:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}兩個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.73,0:13:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.22,0:13:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看來已經得出結論了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.25,0:13:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這樣的話 我還是不幫忙比較好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.75,0:13:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只會妨礙你們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.68,0:13:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}話說這樣的眉目傳情地秀恩愛 還是回宿舍裡去做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.80,0:13:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以真是受不了這些外行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.94,0:13:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你明明很感興趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.52,0:13:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你剛才說什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.73,0:14:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒什麼啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.67,0:14:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}剛才說到的做飯的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.08,0:14:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.01,0:14:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我想和你一起做飯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.16,0:14:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}然後一起吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.67,0:14:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼樣呢 司
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.98,0:14:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}當然了 要不今晚就試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.39,0:14:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你想吃什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.21,0:14:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我好想知道司喜歡吃什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.51,0:14:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是啊 喜歡吃的東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.78,0:14:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 蛋包飯！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.72,0:14:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}像小孩子一樣
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.26,0:14:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司是我正式的搭檔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.47,0:14:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是接替香月的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.66,0:15:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒關係 我大概明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.62,0:15:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}驚喜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.53,0:15:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}驚喜…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.00,0:15:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你有什麼煩心事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.66,0:15:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.57,0:15:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我在想若是要給喜歡的人一個驚喜的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.65,0:15:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼樣的才能讓她高興呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.18,0:15:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你想要讓艾拉高興嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.66,0:15:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.48,0:15:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你太好懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.36,0:15:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.25,0:15:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}「和喜歡的人度過的時光 才是最開心的」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.06,0:15:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉是這麼和我說的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.05,0:15:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以我也覺得也是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.67,0:16:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}話說不管是你還是老爺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.13,0:16:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}笨拙的男性真是多呢
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.12,0:16:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抱歉 讓你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.30,0:16:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒事 有什麼要我幫忙的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.38,0:16:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}現在沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.01,0:16:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有的話就跟你說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.83,0:16:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那時就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.58,0:16:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.12,0:16:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我還算是沒走呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.60,0:16:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不要把我當空氣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.25,0:16:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對不起…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.29,0:16:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.20,0:17:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}太陽下山越來越晚了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.38,0:17:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.49,0:17:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.66,0:17:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.33,0:17:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.91,0:17:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司我想買睡衣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.47,0:17:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯？ 以前是因為沒有才那樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.83,0:17:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}之前一直覺得不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.67,0:17:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 要買情侶裝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.17,0:17:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.11,0:17:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不…倒不是不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.96,0:17:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}肚子餓了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.41,0:17:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}餓了 但是餓著肚子會覺得飯特別好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.46,0:17:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是嗎 真是不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.98,0:17:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我們… 成為戀人了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.09,0:17:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.55,0:18:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是我好像都沒有為艾拉做過什麼特別的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.04,0:18:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我想過許多
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.39,0:18:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可是不知道怎樣才能讓艾拉高興
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.77,0:18:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我只要你像原來那樣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.99,0:18:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}像原來那樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.51,0:18:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只要和司在一起就會很特別了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.47,0:18:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就算是現在 我心情也是小鹿亂撞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.04,0:18:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}心臟好像要爆裂一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.41,0:19:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.20,0:19:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.61,0:19:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在那片光芒下 是不是也有各式各樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.69,0:19:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}像平常一樣生活著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.01,0:19:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我是不是也是其中之一呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.03,0:19:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我們現在這樣才是特別的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.81,0:19:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.31,0:20:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}外觀好微妙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.61,0:20:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我覺得第一次做成這樣已經很不錯啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.67,0:20:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}來畫上喜歡的圖案吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.87,0:20:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.44,0:20:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明明不用劃掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.45,0:20:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}害羞到連我自己都看不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.15,0:20:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那我來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.27,0:20:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是不是有點太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.78,0:20:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那麼 我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.72,0:20:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.83,0:20:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.14,0:20:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.59,0:20:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉也吃吃看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.84,0:21:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.42,0:21:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.48,0:21:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 你又開始寫日記了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.94,0:21:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.17,0:21:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}寫了些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.61,0:21:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不會笑我？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.52,0:21:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不會笑你的
